Hello! Thank you for reaching out to Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. My name is Vincent Richardson. How can I assist you with navigating our website today?

Hi Vincent! I'm just feeling curious about how to explore the yacht listings on your website. My name is Martha Scott.

Nice to meet you, Martha! To start, you can use the search bar at the top of the page. Could you please tell me which type of yachts you are interested in?

I'm curious about sailing yachts. Is there a specific link I should follow?

Yes, Martha. If you click on the 'Yachts for Sale' tab, you'll find a filter option on the left to select 'Sailing Yachts.' Would you also like to receive email updates on new listings?

That sounds great! I'd love to get updates. How do I sign up?

To sign up, I'll first need your email address. Could you spell it out for me?

Sure, it's martha.scott@example.com.

Thank you, Martha. And could you please provide your phone number, just in case we have any special offers or updates?

Certainly, it's five five five, seven eight nine, one two three four.

Perfect, Martha. Thank you for providing that information. You’ll start receiving updates soon. If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out. Thank you for your time today!

Thank you, Vincent. I appreciate your help.
